* name 1..* BackboneElement "Product Name" ""
  * productName 1..1 string "actual name of the product" ""
  * type 1..1  CodeableConcept "type of naming" ""
  * namePart 0..* BackboneElement "selecting parts of name for inteligeble purposes" ""
    * part 1..1 string "part of name" ""
    * type 1..1 CodeableConcept "type of elemente defining -strength, pharmaceutical form, etc" ""
