    * jurisdiction 0..1 CodeableConcept "jurisdiction that applies" ""
    * language 1..1 CodeableConcept "language applicable" ""
* granularity 0..1  CodeableConcept "level of product, substance, pharmaceutical product, medicinal product or packaged medicinal product" ""
